<div class="max-w-2xl pt-24 pb-12 mx-auto sm:pt-32 sm:pb-16">
  <div class="text-center">
    <h1 class="font-serif text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-neutral-900 dark:text-neutral-100 text sm:text-6xl">
      Unleash the True Potential of Your Coffee
    </h1>
    <p class="mt-6 text-lg leading-8 text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-300">
      Elevate your coffee experience by joining our vibrant community of coffee enthusiasts.
      Upload, track, analyze, and perfect your espresso or filter coffee shots with ease.
    </p>
    <div class="flex items-center justify-center mt-10 gap-x-6">
      <% path = user_signed_in? ? shots_path : new_user_registration_path %>
      <%= link_to "Get started", path, class: "submit-button px-3.5 py-2.5" %>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="max-w-5xl px-6 mx-auto lg:px-8">
  <div class="aspect-w-16 aspect-h-9">
    <iframe src="https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/7JPgoQLHvss" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="py-12 sm:py-16">
  <div class="px-6 mx-auto max-w-7xl lg:px-8">
    <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto lg:text-center">
      <h2 class="text-base font-semibold leading-7 text-terracotta-600 dark:text-terracotta-400">Coffee meet Cloud</h2>
      <p class="mt-4 font-serif text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight text-neutral-900 dark:text-neutral-300">Improve Your Coffee</p>
      <p class="mt-6 text-lg leading-8 text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-300">
        Visualizer.coffee offers essential tools and a supportive community to help you explore, perfect, and enjoy your coffee like never before.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto mt-16 sm:mt-20 lg:mt-24 lg:max-w-4xl">
      <dl class="max-w-xl grid grid-cols-1 gap-x-8 gap-y-10 lg:max-w-none lg:grid-cols-2 lg:gap-y-16">
        <div class="relative pl-16">
          <dt class="font-serif text-xl font-bold leading-7 text-neutral-900 dark:text-neutral-300">
            <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 flex items-center justify-center w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-terracotta-600">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 16.5V9.75m0 0l3 3m-3-3l-3 3M6.75 19.5a4.5 4.5 0 01-1.41-8.775 5.25 5.25 0 0110.233-2.33 3 3 0 013.758 3.848A3.752 3.752 0 0118 19.5H6.75z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            Broad Compatibility & Integration
          </dt>
          <dd class="mt-2 text-base leading-7 text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-300">
            Visualizer was designed to work seamlessly with <a href="https://decentespresso.com/" class="underline hover:no-underline" target="_blank">Decent espresso machines</a>.
            Recently, it has expanded its compatibility to support <a href="https://www.naked-portafilter.com/product-category/smart-espresso-profiler/" class="underline hover:no-underline" target="_blank">Smart Espresso Profiler</a>, <a href="https://pressensor.com/" class="underline hover:no-underline" target="_blank">Pressensor</a> and <a href="https://beanconqueror.com/" class="underline hover:no-underline" target="_blank">Beanconqueror</a>.
            This provides a streamlined experience that caters to a diverse range of coffee enthusiasts, accommodating their preferred devices.
          </dd>
        </div>
        <div class="relative pl-16">
          <dt class="font-serif text-xl font-bold leading-7 text-neutral-900 dark:text-neutral-300">
            <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 flex items-center justify-center w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-terracotta-600">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M3.75 3v11.25A2.25 2.25 0 006 16.5h2.25M3.75 3h-1.5m1.5 0h16.5m0 0h1.5m-1.5 0v11.25A2.25 2.25 0 0118 16.5h-2.25m-7.5 0h7.5m-7.5 0l-1 3m8.5-3l1 3m0 0l.5 1.5m-.5-1.5h-9.5m0 0l-.5 1.5m.75-9l3-3 2.148 2.148A12.061 12.061 0 0116.5 7.605" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            Comprehensive Data Analysis
          </dt>
          <dd class="mt-2 text-base leading-7 text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-300">
            Visualizer provides a deep dive into your coffee shots with user-friendly charts and robust comparison tools.
            <%= link_to "Premium", premium_index_path, class: "underline hover:no-underline", target: "_blank" %> users gain access to advanced customization options and a treasure trove of community-generated data to fuel their pursuit of coffee excellence.
          </dd>
        </div>
        <div class="relative pl-16">
          <dt class="font-serif text-xl font-bold leading-7 text-neutral-900 dark:text-neutral-300">
            <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 flex items-center justify-center w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-terracotta-600">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M18 18.72a9.094 9.094 0 003.741-.479 3 3 0 00-4.682-2.72m.94 3.198l.001.031c0 .225-.012.447-.037.666A11.944 11.944 0 0112 21c-2.17 0-4.207-.576-5.963-1.584A6.062 6.062 0 016 18.719m12 0a5.971 5.971 0 00-.941-3.197m0 0A5.995 5.995 0 0012 12.75a5.995 5.995 0 00-5.058 2.772m0 0a3 3 0 00-4.681 2.72 8.986 8.986 0 003.74.477m.94-3.197a5.971 5.971 0 00-.94 3.197M15 6.75a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2.25 2.25 0 11-4.5 0 2.25 2.25 0 014.5 0zm-13.5 0a2.25 2.25 0 11-4.5 0 2.25 2.25 0 014.5 0z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            Connect with a Passionate Community
          </dt>
          <dd class="mt-2 text-base leading-7 text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-300">
            Immerse yourself in a global network of over <%= number_with_delimiter(@user_count) %> coffee aficionados who upload shots daily.
            Engage with fellow coffee enthusiasts, exchange insights, and collaborate in the collective quest for the ultimate coffee.
          </dd>
        </div>
        <div class="relative pl-16">
          <dt class="font-serif text-xl font-bold leading-7 text-neutral-900 dark:text-neutral-300">
            <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 flex items-center justify-center w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-terracotta-600">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M14.25 7.756a4.5 4.5 0 100 8.488M7.5 10.5h5.25m-5.25 3h5.25M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            Flexible Pricing with Exclusive Benefits
          </dt>
          <dd class="mt-2 text-base leading-7 text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-300">
            Access Visualizer for free with a month of saved shots or upgrade to <%= link_to "Premium plan", premium_index_path, class: "underline hover:no-underline", target: "_blank" %> at €5/month for an even richer experience.
            Discover the full range of premium features with a 7-day free trial, and take your coffee journey to new heights.
          </dd>
        </div>
      </dl>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
